Template: custom-conf/host-type
Type: select
Choices: workstation, laptop, server, vserver
Default: vserver
Description: Host type ?
 Please select the host type among the following choices:
 .
  - workstation: user workstation
  - laptop:      user laptop (roaming device)
  - server:      physical server
  - vserver:     virtual server (iow. VServer, OpenVZ, KVM or LXC "guest")

Template: custom-conf/harddisk-type
Type: select
Choices: sata, scsi, pata, virtio
Default: virtio
Description: Harddisk(s) type ?
 Please select the (local) hard-disk(s) type among the following choices:
 .
  - sata: S(erial)-ATA hard-disks
  - scsi: SCSI hard-disks
  - pata: P(lain)-ATA hard-disks
  - virtio: (KVM) VirtIO hard-disks

Template: custom-conf/root-email
Type: string
Default: root@example.org
Description: Root e-mail address ?
 Please specify the e-mail address to which messages addressed to root shall be sent.

